{
  "texts": [
    "And he couldn't help but wonder: was this really the right thing to do?",
    "One day, as Jonah sat under his makeshift shelter, he heard a commotion in the distance.",
    "He looked up to see a group of men approaching him.",
    "They were dressed in fine clothes and carried scrolls in their hands.",
    "The men approached Jonah, their faces filled with reverence."
  ]
}